    <p class="p4"><span class="s2"><b>What is personal data?</b></span></p>
    <p class="p4"><span class="s1">Personal data is any information that relates to or identifies a living individual, both directly or indirectly. This also includes the collection of less explicit data that leads to an identification of a particular person.</span></p>
    <p class="p4"><span class="s2"><b>Collection of Personal Data</b></span></p>
    <p class="p4"><span class="s1">We may collect the following data from the users:</span></p>
    <ol class="ol1">
        <li class="li4"><span class="s1">Personal identification data including age, nationality, date of birth, etc.</span></li>
